These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-1::.
There are 5 different nationalities: polish, canadian, dutch, pakistani, japanese
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, parkour, snowboarding, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the polish is in an odd position##4
4. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
5. the dutch is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |      3       |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | polish    | japanese   | canadian      | pakistani  | dutch    |
| Sport   | handball | weightlifting | snowboarding | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, iris, azalea, rose, balloon-flower
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, roller, snowmobile, tram
 1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5
 2. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
 8. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 9. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
10. the person who growsiris is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the tram##2
11. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |      4      |   5    |
| Flower   | rose   | sunflower     | iris | azalea | balloon-flower    |
| Transport     | motorbike | snowmobile | jet-ski   | tram        | roller |

