.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, mirinda, tea
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, thai, indian, brazilian, spanish
1. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
3. the brazilian is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the thai is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the thai is the thai##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the brazilian##1
8. the russian is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage   | fanta   | cola       | tea         | almond-milk | mirinda |
| Nationality      | indian | thai | russian | brazilian   | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, ritmeester, baccarat, cain, chaman
There are 5 different nationalities: british, canadian, indonesian, italian, russian
 1. the russian is somewhere to the left of the chaman-smoker##5
 2. the british is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 3. the cain-smoker is the italian##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 5. the italian is the cain-smoker##1
 6. the british is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 7. the canadian is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 8. the canadian is in an even position##4
 9. the chaman-smoker is in an odd position##4
10. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the left of the chaman-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Cigar   | cain     | baccarat  | chaman   | ritmeester      | havana  |
| Nationality   | italian | russian | british | canadian | indonesian |

