.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-5::.
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, scrabble, snooker, whist
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, rowing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person playing whist and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
4. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
5. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |   5    |
| Game    | canasta | mah-jongg | scrabble     | snooker     | whist |
| Sport   | skiing  | cycling   | ice-hockey | lacrosse | rowing |

