.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-6::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, fantasy, mystery, superhero
5 different pets are kept: lizard, goat, dog, horse, guinea-pig
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 2. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
 3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 4. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 5. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy | superhero  | crime     | mystery  |
| Pet     | horse    | guinea-pig    | goat | dog | lizard |

