.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, juice, milk, soy-milk
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, lilac, black, green, orange
1. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes green##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
5. the person drinking milk is the person who likes black##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
7. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who likes light-blue##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2   |   3   |     4     |   5   |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk  | fanta | soy-milk  | juice |
| Color   | orange          | black | green | light-blue | lilac   |

