There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, italian, nigerian
1. the person drinking milk is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the australian##1
6. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
7. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking milk and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage          | sprite    | hot-chocolate    | juice | milk | 7up   |
| Nationality   | canadian | italian | australian | nigerian  | argentine |

