 2. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 9. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking mirinda##2
10. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |    5     |
