2. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
9. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage    | tea        | sprite | soy-milk | lemonade   | coffee |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | comedy  | crime     | horror | sports  |

