.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-16::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, magic-tricks, singing, skydiving, traveling
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, turtle, rabbit, dog
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the dog is the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
9. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3       |     4     |    5    |
| Hobby         | hiking  | traveling | magic-tricks | skydiving | singing |
| Pet   | rabbit | turtle   | lizard   | goldfish | dog |

