There 5 different types of food: eggplant, potato, corn, onion, strawberry
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
2. the person eating eggplant is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
4. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
6. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person eating eggplant##5
7. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
8. the person eating potato is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | milk      | iced-tea | mirinda | sprite    | lemonade  |
| Food   | corn | potato   | strawberry | eggplant | onion |

