.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, milk, soy-milk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, disaster, spy, satire, musical
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2       |     3      |      4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk      | soy-milk     | fanta      | coffee       | juice    |
| Movie-Genre        | spy | superhero | disaster | musical | satire |

 